comments: Williams III (BOS) establishes himself in Hill's (CHI) path when incidental contact occurs on the pick.
Hill (CHI) is moving alongside Brown's (BOS) path when marginal body contact occurs on the drive.
Brown (BOS) lifts and replants his pivot foot before passing the ball.
DeRozan (CHI) steps to the side to slip the contact with Brown (BOS) and goes to, and not through Brown.
Schroder (BOS) veers into White's (CHI) path in transition, and the contact is marginal.
White (CHI) moves alongside Schroder's (BOS) path and legally contests his driving shot attempt.
Richardson (BOS) makes contact with the ball prior to making incidental contact with Vucevic (CHI) as he defends the pass.
DeRozan (CHI) is established in Brown's (BOS) path when incidental body contact occurs on the driving shot attempt.
White (CHI) blocks the ball out of bounds. The possession is correctly awarded to (BOS).
Richardson (BOS) is established in Hill's (CHI) path during the screen and as he absorbs the contact, both players briefly engage and separate.
Vucevic (CHI) establishes himself in Tatum's (BOS) path when marginal body contact occurs on the screen.
DeRozan (CHI) and Tatum (BOS) both engage on the perimeter and separate.
Brown (BOS) makes contact with Hill's (CHI) lower body during his upward motion, which affects his body's trajectory and shot attempt.
White (CHI) does not establish himself in Williams III's (BOS) path or give him room to avoid the contact when body contact occurs and affects Williams III's shot.
White (CHI) and Richardson (BOS) make incidental contact off-ball.
Tatum (BOS) legally contests DeRozan's (CHI) jump shot attempt to his side, and any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Vucevic (CHI) grabs Williams III's (BOS) jersey and affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Richardson (BOS) briefly grasps and releases Vucevic's (CHI) jersey. The marginal contact doesn't affect his FOM.
Brown (BOS) legally contests Vucevic's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
Richardson (BOS) legally contests DeRozan's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
